dct_title_s: The Eskimo tribes of north-east America
dct_description_sm: Bureau of Ethnology, Sixth Annual Report. Plate II-III.; "Julius Bien & Co. Lith."; Plate II shows Oqo and Akudnirn, with numbered inset maps of Frobisher Bay, Eclipse Sound and Admiralty Inlet, Repulse Bay and Lyon Inlet, and Boothia Isthmus and King William Land; Plate III shows larger-scale focused on the region of Canada north of Hudson Bay.
